headline: Tilray Brands Introduces Herb & Bloom Non-Alcoholic Beverage
summary: TLRY's innovation efforts are quite on track, with the launch of Herb & Bloom, which is a line of cocktail-inspired ready-to-drink, alcohol-free effervescent beverages.
